text: geudeul-eun yeonhabgun-i ajig tteona ji ani haess-eulila saeng-gaghago iss-eo man-il geu yeonhabgun-i dasi jingyeoghayeo ondamyeon geudeul-eun yulanghaneun yumogmingwa deobul-eo samag-e eunpyehayeo neohuie gwanhayeo algoja hal geos-imyeo man-il geudeul-i neohui gaunde issda haedo geu deul sosuleul je-oehagoneun ssauji anh eulila
